<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Standard boards in 5 different difficulties and 3 different sizes (4 by 4, 9 by 9 and 16 by 16)</li>
<li>Highlighting and hint system</li>
<li>Undo and redo</li>
<li>Board designer for combining multiple boards of varying sizes and filling it using the specified difficulty</li>
<li>Board generation in background for faster serving of new games</li>
</ul>
